Glori:  I don't believe having an answer book makes anything any easier.  And there are plenty of atheist religious texts around that will provide you with whatever moral code you choose.  [And &quot;atheist religious&quot; wasn't an error.]<br>
<br>
Merentha:  My statement wasn't directed at you.  I've just gotten that one a lot over the many years I've been involved in religious debates.  It's terribly humorous to hear someone tell me I'm wrong, and then tell me I'm close-minded.  And it's even funnier when they refuse to recognize how they are more so than me.  I at least listened and weighed their ideas before deciding they were in error.<br>
<br>
Iwka:  My life is anything but boring.  To suggest otherwise merely because I'm a believer (similar to Glori's claim that it's easier for the same reason) is pretty shallow.  And to critique all of Christendom because one professed believer is a lunatic, is neither fair nor rational.  &quot;Guilt by association&quot; isn't usually acceptable.<br>
<br>
Chit:  Just because the Supremes say you can't be prosecuted for something, doesn't mean that it is right to do it.  I'm not a fanatical patriot in any respect, but flag burning is wrong.  It may be legal, but it's still wrong.  You've espoused similar feelings as I recall on a few subjects (abortion being one, although I may be wrong).  Why not recognize this one?<br>
<br>
Why do people care about the Confederate Flag, for the exact reason we care about the American Flag:  &quot;for which it stands.&quot;  The Confederate Flag stands for slavery in the eyes of most Americans (those that say it stands for states rights are either fooling themselves or trying to fool others).  To govern under a flag devoted to slavery taints the action of all those in the state.  The boycott against SC is a very good way of hitting politicians where it hurts, the budget and the warchest. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#666666><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub4.ezboard.com/uchiteng.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Chiteng</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/globalBlack.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Veteran</span><br>  Posts: 1245<br> <font color=#E9D756>(7/1/02 10:53:16 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub4.ezboard.com/femarrdragonsandplanes.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=3442.topic&index=170>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Raedwulf</span><hr size=1> Well you see I have to say I am too old for that kind of militant confrontation.<br>
